title: Large RV/Trailer Sites@Wine Country RV Park in Rohnert Park
map_address: 7450 Cristobal Way near East Cotati Ave
posting_body: ['Please read below for alternative RV Space size options.', 'Located near the South Entrance of Sonoma State University, and serving the general public.', "This long-term-stay RV Park was originally established in the early 1970's to provide students attending Sonoma State with off-campus-housing.", 'Between our comfortable lodge-style community building, two bath-houses, included basic cable, and included basic WIFI; you can truly minimize your expenses.', 'Water, Sewer, and Garbage are also included.', 'We have re-opened some of the parks smallest spaces for the first time in years:', "SMALL: they can only fit a 19' maximum or some even less over-all-length RV.", 'Our Spaces are:', "Small (13' to 19') @ $1,150.00/month*", 'Security Deposit $1,150.00', "Large (20' to 35') @ $1,350.00/month*", 'Security Deposit $1,350.00', '(Security Deposit may vary depending on credit/rental history)', '$100.00 Electrical Deposit, Tenant pays for their sites metered electricity usage.', "***** Move in special $1.00 dollar pays for 1st month's rent ******", 'Upon your being approved, we may enter into a Holding Deposit Agreement that will reserve your RV space for you until the move-in date.', 'Please call us at', 'show contact info', 'now!', 'You may also reply through this Craigslist AD to receive an application, or, apply online at <URL> or feel free to stop by, we are open Monday-Saturday 9am-6pm and Sunday by appointment only.', 'Applications are to be filled out by all applicants, over the age of 18', 'Application fee $30', "Make a Cashier's Check or Money Order, payable to: 7450 Cristobal Way LP"]
